    <refsection>
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>
            <literal>beep()</literal> produit le son "beep".
        </para>
        <para>
            <literal>beep('on')</literal> active le "beep"
        </para>
        <para>
            <literal>beep('off')</literal> desactive le "beep"
        </para>
        <para>
            <literal>s=beep()</literal> retourne le mode courantreturns the current beep
            mode (on or off).
        </para>
    </refsection>
